{
  "stem": "1292.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I-- the kidneys was damaged throughout-- through such-- or lungs, or whatever, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you'd have to stand up and say, thank you, and say their name, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some just-- After they were beaten?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Goth.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Goth did give the order to do it-- to-- and a lot of Ukrainians usually did exercise this punishment, Ukrainian soldiers, which was what they called volksdeutsche-- if you heard of it-- that-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ah!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is a torture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're filming all this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, in the camp, there was different work, compulsory different work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I did work in a werkstatte, what was called, Schlosserei.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a barrack in-- in a-- in a concentration camp, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was some which was working at-- they was breaking some mountains and-- well, detonation, yes?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is that what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there wasn't any-- there wasn't any security for their injuries or anything like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So very often, a leg would be torn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, I did see a lovely girl who-- whose leg was torn off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- oh, God.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was bleeding to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before they did-- could give her any aid-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --and there was different werkstattes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was some-- what we'd sew uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was some which did make brushes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what were you actually doing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was partially in a office of that Schlosserei.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that Goth, he would come without any-- well, people did try not to work hard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would come without any warning and ask, how many of this did you make?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Make one for me so I see, yeah?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he would make one.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
